==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Colter
<hw>Col"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>culter</ets>, fr. L. <ets>culter</ets> plowshare, knife. Cf.
<er>Cutlass</er>.]</ety> <def>A knife or cutter, attached to the beam of
a plow to cut the sward, in advance of the plowshare and
moldboard.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>coulter</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coltish</ent>⟦br⟧
